        <li>Modifying or copying the materials</li>
        <li>Using the materials for any commercial purpose or for any public display</li>
        <li>Attempting to decompile or reverse engineer any software contained on the website</li>
        <li>Removing any copyright or other proprietary notations from the materials</li>
        <li>Transferring the materials to another person or "mirroring" the materials on any other server</li>
        <li>Using the materials in any way that is unlawful or in violation of any applicable law or regulation</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 mt-12">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        The materials on FunGab Global's website are provided "as is". FunGab Global makes no warranties, expressed or implied, and hereby disclaims and negates all other warranties including, without limitation, implied warranties or conditions of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement of intellectual property or other violation of rights.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 mt-12">Limitations</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        In no event shall FunGab Global or its suppliers be liable for any damages (including, without limitation, damages for loss of data or profit, or due to business interruption) arising out of the use or inability to use the materials on FunGab Global's website, even if FunGab Global or an authorized representative has been notified orally or in writing of the possibility of such damage.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 mt-12">Accuracy of Materials</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        The materials appearing on FunGab Global's website could include technical, typographical, or photographic errors. FunGab Global does not warrant that any of the materials on its website are accurate, complete, or current. FunGab Global may make changes to the materials contained on its website at any time without notice.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 mt-12">Links</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        FunGab Global has not reviewed all of the sites linked to its website and is not responsible for the contents of any such linked site. The inclusion of any link does not imply endorsement by FunGab Global of the site. Use of any such linked website is at the user's own risk.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 mt-12">Modifications</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        FunGab Global may revise these terms of service for its website at any time without notice. By using this website, you are agreeing to be bound by the then current version of these terms of service.
      </p>

